{"tid":1797771,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想學電腦繪畫 插畫 有冇好介紹？","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T06:21:44.000Z","uid":327486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35e64279da34b2c5429aa66ba971498945d513cd","tid":1797771,"uid":327486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4V09BN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4V09BN.jpg&h=16cc1ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfcZFJs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfcZFJs.jpg&h=fcea8bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想學畫畫<br />\n0技巧<br />\n拎支鉛筆跟住畫都畫到鬼五馬六<br />\n想學畫畫黎自己畫呢隻野<br />\n為自己興趣<br />\n係唔係都要由素描開始學？<br />\n就咁睇呢隻小熊好似好簡單<br />\n但係要畫得自然畫得靚<br />\n一定要落苦功<br />\n所以我想跟人學<br />\n<br />\n呢類畫畫要係電腦上面畫<br />\n請問市面有冇教人學電腦繪畫 <br />\n有冇好介紹？ <br />\nFreelance 教唔教人畫畫架<br />\n <br />\n唔該曬巴打絲打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBmPiwf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBmPiwf.png&h=85d76e21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nO7SghV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnO7SghV.jpg&h=4e2188b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4e1a36ea82186df5b526e829c71badf3d6300de","tid":1797771,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"lm學"},{"pid":"61f186591590c35697f4ebaea8ace2277b621001","tid":1797771,"uid":327486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e1a36ea82186df5b526e829c71badf3d6300de","tid":1797771,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"lm學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"呢d幾可愛幾清新<br />\n所以想學"},{"pid":"8f7535df4ca38058d61772fdb3850e9d990551de","tid":1797771,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"edf